consultancy reports earnings for the six months ended March 31.
The shares were unchanged at 1.60 rand.  Value Group Ltd. (VLE)  : The transport and logistics
provider reports results for the year ended Feb. 28. It said on
April 28 earnings per share will be as much as 20 percent higher
than in the year-earlier period. The shares were unchanged at
